description: The Barone Meatball Company is serving up a gourmet twist on this classic Italian comfort food. Not only does their menu feature the traditional Italian seasoned beef meatball smothered in marinara, but it also features lamb meatballs, buffalo chicken meatballs, chicken parmesan meatballs, seafood meatballs, and veggie meatballs! Grab a side of mac n cheese, cole slaw, or a variety of salads.
name: Barone Meatball Company
